title: Did Real Clear Politics Take Penn. ‘Away’ From Biden After Lawsuit News?
subtitle: It is challenging to take something away that was never given in the first place.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Media outlet Real Clear Politics projected Joe Biden to win Pennsylvania in the 2020 U.S. presidential election but rescinded that call after news of a lawsuit that could "invalidate 300,000 or more" Democratic votes.
